features.text: A dark enchanted mushroom offers wishes to nature. 1/1 animated 3D render by Poison Garden

The Baron's glance falls upon thee suddenly: through skeletal mask his eyes meet yours with a cold gaze, his regal posture holding the grandeur of seven almighty’s on high. Both savage and refined. Perhaps he knows you are wondering what lays behind his striking visage.

#1/1 original 80x120cm painting by Eric Hanu

Deafening is the silence of The Baroness as she stands cloaked the in blackest of garb with no eyes to meet even in fear. Rows of teeth sit beneath a hockey mask adorned as a face which gazes back at you with only nothingness. Her skin a chilling blue, is cold even to look on, with horns reaching untoward the heavens. The centre chest holds an old jewel, her heart… growing more brittle and icy with each passing second.

#1/1 original 80x120cm painting by Eric Hanu
